	(text "IDRIVE: Mosfet Drive Current\n	Target: 300ns Rise, 100ns Fall\n	Gate-Drain Charge: 7.9nC\n		Rise: 7.9nC / 300ns = 30mA -> 18kΩ to AGND\n		Fall: 7.9nC / 150ns = 60mA -> 18kΩ to AGND\n\nMODE: PWM input mode\n	3-PWM -> Mode 1 -> 47kΩ to AGND\n\nGAIN: Current Sense Gain\n	20 V/V -> 47k to GND\n	40 V/V -> Pull-Up\n	5 V/V  -> Pull-Dowm\n\nVDS: Overcurrent Protection\n	Max Current > 35A\n	RDSon@100°C = 0.00516Ω\n		Overcurrent Voltage = 35A * 5.16mΩ = 0.1806V\n		Choose 0.26V -> 75kΩ to AGND\n		Actual Overcurrent@125°C = 0.26V / 5.16mΩ ~ 50.39A"
